definitions.definition: The female genitalia , especially the vulva .
An extremely unpleasant or objectionable person (in US, especially a woman; in Commonwealth more usually a man).

examples: Fix the car? I’ll sort the cunt out at the weekend.

definitions.definition: An unpleasant or difficult experience or incident.
A woman or any receptive sexual partner, as a source of potential or actual sexual gratification.
examples: I'm going to hit the clubs and see if I can get me some cunt .

definitions.definition: A person (mostly between male friends); compare bastard .
examples: Yes, I do remember Dave; he was one funny cunt .
Tom's a good cunt : he fixed my car and didn't even charge me for it!
